  <entry key="landing.hero.title">Where Design Meets Digital Precision</entry>
  <entry key="landing.hero.subtitle">Experience furniture in photorealistic 3D before it enters your space. Powered by real-time ray tracing and spatial computing.</entry>
  <entry key="landing.hero.enter_showroom">Enter Showroom</entry>
  <entry key="landing.hero.live_demo">Live Demo</entry>
