  <entry key="landing.fidelity.title">Ultra-High Fidelity</entry>
  <entry key="landing.fidelity.subtitle">Precision in Every Pixel</entry>
  <entry key="landing.fidelity.description">Our rendering pipeline captures sub-millimeter surface details, accurate material reflections, and physically correct lighting. Every texture, grain, and contour is reproduced with scientific accuracy.</entry>
  <entry key="landing.fidelity.feature1.title">Ray-Traced Lighting</entry>
  <entry key="landing.fidelity.feature1.desc">Physically accurate light simulation with global illumination, caustics, and volumetric scattering for photorealistic material rendering.</entry>
  <entry key="landing.fidelity.feature2.title">Micro-Texture Analysis</entry>
  <entry key="landing.fidelity.feature2.desc">Sub-pixel surface scanning captures wood grain, fabric weave, and metal patina at 8K resolution for tactile visual fidelity.</entry>
