  <entry key="landing.steps.title">From Scan to Sanctuary</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step1.title">Spatial Scan</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step1.desc">Our LiDAR-powered scanner maps your room in 30 seconds, creating a precise digital twin with accurate dimensions and lighting conditions.</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step2.title">AI Curation</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step2.desc">Machine learning analyzes your space, existing furniture, and style preferences to recommend pieces that complement your environment.</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step3.title">Photorealistic Preview</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step3.desc">See furniture in your actual room with ray-traced lighting, accurate shadows, and material interactions before purchasing.</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step4.title">White Glove Delivery</entry>
  <entry key="landing.steps.step4.desc">Professional installation team places each piece exactly as positioned in your digital preview, ensuring perfect placement.</entry>
